description:
There are a million moving parts to making a great game. Heroes project manager Arnaldo Oliveira and solutions architect Jader Feijo talk about the worldwide team, innovative tech and cost-cutting solutions that were needed to make both the original Heroes and Heroes 2 a reality.

How did they go from concept to product? How did they stretch their budgets? How did they handle naysayers? What was hardest about creating Heroes? What was most rewarding?

Arnaldo and Jader get into this and more in this inspiring behind-the-scenes look at the making of Heroes.

Learn more at: https://www.heroesbibletrivia.org/en/
